# Frontend styling (this project)

- **SCSS** via Vite — entry `resources/scss/app.scss`. Run builds with **`ddev bun`**.
- **No Tailwind** — do not add `tailwindcss`, `@tailwindcss/vite`, or utility-class styling.
- **BEM** class names in markup; **one** `resources/scss/components/_{block}.scss` partial per component.
- Creode adaptability rules: query **Creode Documentation MCP** (`creode-web-components` skill) — do not duplicate those docs here.
- Follow `.cursor/skills/frontend-scss/SKILL.md` for repo structure.
